### Goods - Create
POST {{SkyRoc_HostAddress}}/api/Goods
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "奶油生菜",
  "code": "GOODS_LETTUCE_001",
  "goodsTypeId": "{{goodsTypeId}}",
  "defaultSupplierId": "{{supplierId}}",
  "defaultWareId": "{{wareId}}",
  "spec": "500g/份",
  "origin": "北京",
  "taxRate": 9,
  "isOnSale": true,
  "supplierIds": [
    "{{supplierId}}"
  ],
  "status": 1
}

### Goods - Update
PUT {{SkyRoc_HostAddress}}/api/Goods
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "{{goodsId}}",
  "name": "精品奶油生菜",
  "code": "GOODS_LETTUCE_001",
  "goodsTypeId": "{{goodsTypeId}}",
  "baseUnitId": "{{goodsUnitId}}",
  "defaultSupplierId": "{{supplierId}}",
